heal [level 5]: the basic heal spell.  
                 healer can cast on any living being. 
                 healer gains some xp for healing others. 
                 note: hp/sp are to heal only hp or sp
                 
                 syntax:  heal <target> <amount>
                          hp <target> <amount>
                          sp <target> <amount>
                
                note: <amount> is optional 
                      if you do not put in an amount your max healing
                      ability will occur
                          
                 cost:  sp: the amount you healed       
                 